key.radenchants:category.title: Rad Enchants
itemGroup.radenchants.name: Rad Enchants
enchantment.radenchants.life_leech.desc: Heals the user for a portion of damage dealt
enchantment.radenchants.magical_blade.de: Converts a portion of damage to magic

enchantment.radenchants.safeguard.desc: Gains charges over time that completely blocks attacks
enchantment.radenchants.gluttony.desc: Consume food faster with reduced nutritional value

enchantment.radenchants.sheathed.desc: Item is drawn immediately when hurt

enchantment.radenchants.recoil.desc: Attacks on your shield propel you away from the attacker
enchantment.radenchants.evasive_fire.des: After shooting, evade away from nearby enemies
enchantment.radenchants.focus_fire.desc: Shooting with no enemies nearby increases damage
enchantment.radenchants.ruthless.desc: Low health enemies take increased damage
enchantment.radenchants.one_man_army.des: Damage increases based on how many monsters are nearby

enchantment.radenchants.pocket_protector: Grants access to Ender Chest via a keybind

message.radenchants:insomnia: You can't seem to fall asleep
message.radenchants:good_dream: You've had a good night's slumber!

enchantment.radenchants.shadow_meld.desc: Hiding in shadows grants invisibility and speed boost
enchantment.radenchants.paladin.desc: When nearby players are harmed, transfers a portion of their damage to you
enchantment.radenchants.one_with_the_bla: Having only your sword boosts damage

message.radenchants:snitch.dimension.res: Target is not in same dimension

enchantment.radenchants.glare.desc: You stare daggers at enemies, harming those who lock eyes with you
enchantment.radenchants.socketed.desc: Magically enhances the qualities of an item

tooltip.radenchants.sockets.info.stars: > Stars (%s): 1 = 90%%+ Stat Roll, 2 = 100%% Stat Roll, 3 = 100%% Stat Roll and 100%% Upgrade Roll

enchantment.radenchants.sacrifice.desc: Killing your tamed animals empowers you
enchantment.radenchants.earplugs.desc: Use the '/earplugs' command to muffle sounds. You can muffle a sound directory instead of one sound, for example: 'minecraft:entity.cow' instead of each entry.
enchantment.radenchants.climbing_gear.de: Allows rapid climbing of ladders, and fast travel with right-click
